query:
INSERT INTO match_rule (
                name, match_string, order_index ,transaction_type_id
            ) VALUES ($1, $2, 
                (SELECT COUNT(*)+1 FROM match_rule),
                $3::text::uuid) 
            RETURNING 
                id::text as "id!",
                name,
                match_string as "pattern",
                transaction_type_id::text as "transaction_type_id!"
